text: The National Party of Australia (WA), also called the WA Nationals, is the Western Australian branch of the National Party, a centre-right agrarian party in Australia. It is the senior partner in the Coalition with the Liberal Party, which is currently in Opposition. The current leader of the party is Shane Love and its deputy leader is Peter Rundle.
